00:35:13.500 --> 00:35:14.380
I like it.

00:35:14.500 --> 00:35:15.220
It's good.

00:35:16.380 --> 00:35:18.220
Web Developer Toolbar.

00:35:18.340 --> 00:35:19.220
Oh, my word.

00:35:19.380 --> 00:35:20.100
Oh, my word.

00:35:20.380 --> 00:35:26.340
We use the near legendary
Web Developer Toolbar to perform all sorts of tasks,

00:35:26.620 --> 00:35:30.620
