00:35:34.140 --> 00:35:35.100
It's quite nice.

00:35:35.220 --> 00:35:37.300
You can validate local HTML

00:35:37.420 --> 00:35:40.260
so if you are developing locally
as you as you should.

00:35:40.700 --> 00:35:44.340
You've got your web server
installed on your laptop.

00:35:44.500 --> 00:35:48.700
