00:36:07.540 --> 00:36:11.220
Document outline checking,
semantic ordering,

00:36:11.420 --> 00:36:17.100
tab indexes,
unlabeled form fields.

00:36:17.260 --> 00:36:19.020
Literally, the list goes on.

00:36:19.260 --> 00:36:24.300
This is the proper Swiss army knife
for millions

00:36:24.540 --> 00:36:26.580
of different things in one extension.

00:36:27.580 --> 00:36:30.260
I just want to be really clear,

00:36:30.420 --> 00:36:32.700
if there's one extension
that everyone should install,

00:36:32.860 --> 00:36:34.700
genuinely, it's that one.

00:36:34.860 --> 00:36:37.500
It's available for a number
of different browsers.

00:36:38.100 --> 00:36:41.460
Contrast quick checks.

00:36:41.580 --> 00:36:44.580
Obviously,
I've mentioned automated tools here,

00:36:44.740 --> 00:36:47.660
but we use this one here.

00:36:47.860 --> 00:36:51.900
That is very clearly
called Colour Contrast Checker.

00:36:51.980 --> 00:36:55.340
They have a website
