00:37:00.940 --> 00:37:03.500
This allows us
to just quickly do

00:37:03.620 --> 00:37:06.060
on the spot assessments
of color contrast

00:37:06.220 --> 00:37:08.700
of our designs
or websites or anything.

00:37:08.820 --> 00:37:11.460
Has a nice little eye dropper
where you can sample colors.

00:37:11.660 --> 00:37:14.060
It's actually very, very nice.

00:37:14.220 --> 00:37:16.140
This tool helps ensure

00:37:16.260 --> 00:37:20.620
