contrast requirements for accessibility.

00:37:20.820 --> 00:37:23.020
As I say, I think it looks great.

00:37:23.180 --> 00:37:25.940
It also has a nice trick up its sleeve,

00:37:26.100 --> 00:37:29.700
which enables you
