00:45:33.780 --> 00:45:37.820
I asked to work with someone
who at least made an online course,

00:45:37.980 --> 00:45:40.180
but I don't think this is going to happen.

00:45:40.340 --> 00:45:43.460
Should I take the responsibility
in the design too?

00:45:43.620 --> 00:45:46.300
That's a really, really interesting question.

00:45:46.540 --> 00:45:49.540
I've actually spent most of my career

00:45:49.620 --> 00:45:52.700
before joining Illustrate Digital
as a freelancer

00:45:52.900 --> 00:45:55.100
