00:45:55.260 --> 00:46:03.060
With this one,
it really depends on your client

00:46:03.220 --> 00:46:05.660
or the agency you're working with, Philip.

00:46:05.820 --> 00:46:13.940
For me, I would offer to collaborate

00:46:14.100 --> 00:46:19.060
with their in-house design team
right from the start.

00:46:19.300 --> 00:46:24.980
You may also offer them the choice
of collaboration and consultation.

00:46:25.460 --> 00:46:26.860
It's up to you how you build that.

00:46:26.980 --> 00:46:28.500
Of course, I'm not going to get into that.

00:46:28.620 --> 00:46:32.940
Collaboration and fostering that
